Package base_SOM_Objects.som_examples

Class SOM_FtrDataBoundMonitor

java.lang.Object
base_SOM_Objects.som_examples.SOM_FtrDataBoundMonitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
SOM_GeomFtrBndMon
public abstract class SOM_FtrDataBoundMonitor extends Object
this class will manage a single data bound multi-dim array, consisting of ftr arrays for min, max, diff, count, etc. idxs are as follows : 1st idx is what type of examples are being aggregated - this will be specified by the instancing class 2nd idx is min/max/diff, etc; last example is ftr idx in source data
